Sec. 1. 33 V.S.A. § 1901n is added to read:
§ 1901n. HIGH-INTENSITY RESIDENTIAL TREATMENT FOR
SUBSTANCE USE DISORDER AND CO-OCCURRING
MENTAL CONDITIONS

